description:
America’s most eligible, Becca Kufrin (THE BACHELORETTE), is here for this week’s episode of Unqualified! First, Becca and Anna talk about making girl friends in college and play a round of dating deal breakers. Then, they discuss what it’s like to constantly be in the public eye and how her family felt about her very public breakup. After that, Becca gives us some insight into the process of filming The Bachelorette before they call Erin, whose Bumble match keeps making excuses not to meet her, and Megan, who has a massive crush on a guy at her gym. Tune in and enjoy, dear listeners!
